snippet.title: RoboDunk Prologue Trailer - Roguelite Basketball Combat Robots
snippet.description:
The ROBODUNK prologue is out now! It's a roguelite basketball combat game with toy brick robots. 
PLAY IT NOW:  ⇨⇨ https://s.team/a/2385890/ ⇦⇦
Can you beat the Robot Masters and steal their skills with your sky-high dunks, satisfying tackles and explosive weapons? An exclusive single player and coop challenge not in the main game, + classic 4 players versus. Is DUNK the meaning of life?

WISHLIST: https://store.steampowered.com/app/15...
WEBSITE: https://robodunk.com
DISCORD: https://discord.robodunk.com

ORIGINAL ROBOT DESIGNS:
MittenNinja (https://www.flickr.com/photos/mittenninja/)
A. YATES (https://www.flickr.com/photos/ekil)

Chubbybots (https://www.youtube.com/user/chubbybots)
Alex Howe (https://www.flickr.com/photos/jandyman/11742551236/)
